"or (extended) config keys.\n"
"\n"
"Commas between consecutive shorthand chars are optional.\n"
"\n"
"Pre-defined column shorthand chars:\n"
"  h - Hostname\n"
"  m - MAC Address\n"
"  i - IP Address\n"
"  t - Type\n"
"  L - Location of the DHCP Lease (e.g. its cluster member)"
